.TH wxStatusBar 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxStatusBar \- A status bar is a narrow window that can be placed along the bottom of a frame to give small amounts of status information.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
It can contain one or more fields, one or more of which can be variable length according to the size of the window.

.PP
\fIwxStatusBar\fR also maintains an independent stack of status texts for each field (see \fIpushStatusText/3\fR and \fIpopStatusText/2\fR).

.PP
Note that in \fIwxStatusBar\fR context, the terms \fIpane\fR and \fIfield\fR are synonyms.

.SS "Styles"

.PP
